description: Urban Television Network Corporation operates a broadcast television network. The company provides various broadcasting and digital streaming services, as well as operates movie studio. It also offers URBT-TV, a cable and broadcast television network, for the conservative voices of America and airs; and URBTPlus, a digital internet streaming subscription-based service, that provides video-on-demand movies and live streaming television worldwide for a monthly fee based on the plan. Urban Television Network Corporation was incorporated in 1986 and is based in Santa Fe Springs, California.
